      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just too much to deal with. i don't even want to talk to someone on a phone line, they're just gonna tell me it'll be okay or that money isn't everything. but it is everything. my whole life was built on that. everything i planned for, everyone i was supposed to take care of... it's all gone. i feel like i've already died, honestly. like the person i was this morning doesn't even exist anymore. there's nothing left to go back to.",
